              },
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "H.Hirabayashi et al., mention that the obtained",
                "averaged cross section 8.1+-0.19 mb at 12 GeV is",
                "nearly equal to 7.92+-0.18 mb at 28 GeV obtained by",
                "J.B Cumming et al. Therefore the present results",
                "support Cumming's remark the cross section is nearly",
                "constant in the energy region of 10-30 GeV."
              ]
            }
